                <h1>Void Function Usage</h1>
                <p>A void function is a function that doesn't return any value. It's typically used when the function performs a task without needing to return any result.</p>
                <pre><code>void greet() {
            printf("Hello, World!\n");
        }</code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

